---
title: Pan-Seared Fish & North Indian Coconut Sauce with Garlic-Soy Veggies & Basmati Rice
description: Our rich North Indian-spiced coconut sauce is a stellar way to bring fish to your dinner table. It's full of aromatic flavours and ready in less than 30 minutes. To make the perfect rice, avoid the temptation to lift the lid before it's ready – it cooks in its own steam!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mumbai-style-coconut-fish-curry-22c2a7e7.jpg
